---
TEMPLATE VARIABLES (placeholders {{variable}})
---
Use format {{variable_name}} in template_content.
Variables are replaced at generate/export time.

**From content_planners:**
  post_title         - Post title
  content_description - Content description
  platform           - Platform (Instagram, TikTok, etc)
  division           - Division
  post_type          - Post type
  hashtags           - Hashtags
  target_location    - Target location
  goal               - Content goal
  keywords           - Keywords
  week               - Week (date)

**From companies (via planner):**
  company_name       - Company name
  brand_voice        - Brand voice
  target_audience    - Target audience
  tone               - Communication tone

**From ai_results:**
  result_text        - Main content text (from AI)
  result_caption     - Social media caption (from AI)
  result_image_prompt - Prompt for AI image generation (for template type image)
                        Consumed when generating image from AI.